OL,3,CManchester United face legal action
OL,4,Cover historic sexual abuse allegations
OL,6,FManchester United is facing legal
OL,7,Faction over allegations their former
OL,8,Fcaretaker subjected the claimant to
OL,9,F"sexual and physical abuse when he was
OL,10,Fa child".
OL,12,FThe civil claim relates to Billy
OL,13,FWatts, a former caretaker and
OL,14,Fgroundsman at the club's Cliff
OL,15,Ftraining ground in Salford during the
OL,16,F1980s.
