OL,3,CManchester United face legal action
OL,4,Cover historic sexual abuse allegations
OL,6,FWatts died in 2009, but the claim
OL,7,Falleges Manchester United failed to
OL,8,Fprotect the claimant, who cannot be
OL,9,Fnamed for legal reasons, from abuse
OL,10,Fwhile he was under the club's care and
OL,11,Fsupervision.
OL,13,FThe claimant is being represented by
OL,14,FSimpson Millar Solicitors, who say
OL,15,Fwinning the case would serve as both
OL,16,F"a formal recognition of the harm
OL,17,Fsuffered and a means of accessing
OL,18,Fessential support".
