OL,4,Cover historic sexual abuse allegations
OL,6,FKate Hall, Abuse Law Expert at Simpson
OL,7,FMillar, said: "Our client has shown
OL,8,Fenormous courage in coming forward
OL,9,Fafter so many years. He, like many
OL,10,Fsurvivors, has had to relive
OL,11,Fincredibly painful memories in order
OL,12,Fto seek justice."
OL,14,FIn 2021 Manchester United told the
OL,15,FSheldon Review, which investigated
OL,16,Fallegations of historic sexual abuse
OL,17,Fon behalf of the Football Association,
OL,18,Fthat in 2016 the club was made aware
OL,19,Fof several accusations that a
OL,20,Fcaretaker behaved inappropriately
OL,21,Fbehaviour during the 1980s.
