OL,6,FSimpson Millar claim Watts is the
OL,7,Fcaretaker mentioned in the Sheldon
OL,8,FReview.
OL,10,FThe report states that he allegedly
OL,11,F"made inappropriate comments of a
OL,12,Fsexual nature, physically pulled an
OL,13,Findividual into an office against his
OL,14,Fwill, followed an individual into a
OL,15,Fsauna at the training ground and
OL,16,Fwrestled with him."
