OL,6,FThe report goes on to say: "There was
OL,7,Falso an allegation that the caretaker
OL,8,Fhad tried to touch another individual
OL,9,Finappropriately in the showers... the
OL,10,Fcaretaker had tried to touch another
OL,11,Fboy, and when confronted had said that
OL,12,F'I'm only messing, shut up'."
OL,14,FAn investigation was launched into the
OL,15,Fcaretaker in the 1980s, and he was re-
OL,16,Fdeployed from the training grounds to
OL,17,FOld Trafford.
