OL,6,FThe firm has hit out at Manchester
OL,7,FUnited with claims the club has so far
OL,8,F"declined to engage with the legal
OL,9,Fprocess".
OL,11,FIt added: "While Manchester United
OL,12,Fcontributed to the Sheldon Review, its
OL,13,Fapproach to this legal claim has been
OL,14,Fdisappointing. Survivors deserve more
OL,15,Fthan sympathy`they deserve meaningful
OL,16,Fengagement and accountability."
