OL,6,FSimpson Millar also claimed the case
OL,7,F"exposes a clear gap between the
OL,8,Fpublic commitments made by
OL,9,Finstitutions following historic abuse
OL,10,Finquiries and their private handling
OL,11,Fof individual claims".
OL,13,FAt the time of the Sheldon Review, a
OL,14,Fstatement issued by United said: "We
OL,15,Fhave cooperated fully with the Sheldon
OL,16,Freview in an effort to make sure we
OL,17,Fwere as comprehensive on this
OL,18,Fimportant matter as we could be. This
OL,19,Finvolved conducting multiple
OL,20,Finterviews as part of our wide-ranging
OL,21,Fenquiries pursuant to the review."
